      <title>日本银行对员工进行新情况培训：正利率</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/japanese-bank-trains-staff-novel-scenario-positive-interest-rates-2024-03-18/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着日本接近结束八年的负利率，京都的一家地区贷款机构正在提供电子学习，以培训没有在正利率环境下放贷或吸收存款经验的员工。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/japanese-bank-trains-staff-novel-scenario-positive-interest-rates-2024-03-18/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 03:02:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
